1T07:20:47.000Z","msg":"新手就一pair 15kg 先啦 唔好練太重"},{"pid":"ed8361b86846e1bb08a43eae1c2ad75a06bf6d0b","tid":2045324,"uid":140666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9972d6e58ba7034457ee5e5f624549839e04f58d","tid":2045324,"uid":142225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:25:08.000Z","msg":"見依家啲gym room開返 心郁郁想去玩下 操大隻啲<br />\n但係之前又冇做過gym同去過gym room<br />\n身邊又冇frd做gym <br />\n想問下join邊間好啲 同埋跟咩youtube片好 因為驚整親<br />\n仲有係咪要食蛋白粉 邊到有得買 邊隻好<br />\n有啲咩新手應該注意下 <br />\n同埋係咪要自己帶啞鈴？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求解答"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T07:31:58.000Z","msg":"康文署最好"},{"pid":"be0edf3f43c5f58bb3a5841bcd598700d4f39549","tid":2045324,"uid":56875,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"新手建議你唔洗買啞鈴住，因為怕你三分鍾熱度，你可以從壓上掌開始入手，頭一個月每日做3SET，每SET 5下，等你身體適應咗先加上去。<br />\n唔好飲蛋白粉，去飲Gainer，新手最好增磅先，而且蜜月期易吸收，最好一日飲7杯Gainer，到你一個月後，先買啞鈴修線條。"},{"pid":"a6d0b2d4a7f7690dec7a1094ca72153a110eee54","tid":2045324,"uid":119688,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T08:27:43.000Z","msg":"每個動作做一兩手下就足夠<br />\n好易大隻<br />\n太大隻就唔好睇"},{"pid":"a123825588e36b3c82721dd2913c309ced01a6c4","tid":2045324,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"康文就可以<br />\n唔該"},{"pid":"5387da97641eb0f9d00057763246e7063ca3761f","tid":2045324,"uid":308271,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4fcd5f0f924764179955bb97677796c9e2012aff","tid":2045324,"uid":4767,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"ff74959f9c48cdc60c498ef95e0baf5ac134de48","tid":2045324,"uid":142225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be9a1a8789facd71b8d699c8b5f6941e10e6f6bd","tid":2045324,"uid":340192,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T17:34:33.000Z","msg":"季候鳥